{"tid":2261014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[UFO?][玩燈?]凌晨3點上空見到不明光線","createTime":"2020-10-28T04:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T06:09:04.000Z","uid":301632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6fa9f06bb6fcee40557df0970cdf4b74a28904","tid":2261014,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXC7kuF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXC7kuF.jpg&h=a92bd91e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋晚3點青衣<br />\n未訓着望咗出窗 <br />\n突然見到啲照向上天<br />\n啲光Area好大<br />\n其間向外散 再照翻中心 loop咗幾次<br />\n啲顏色又綠又橙 好似仲有幾隻色 不停閃<br />\n好似燈光show咁<br />\n當時有拎手機拍 但拍片 手機自動拉到好暗 <br />\n乜都影唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來回幾下之後又熄咗<br />\n<br />\n之後一直捕住 <br />\n點知真係又着<br />\n今次5條光束 如圖1<br />\n全白<br />\n過多陣又熄<br />\n最後又着 今次白藍咁閃 不過比第一次慢好多<br />\n如圖2<br />\n最後就熄晒 我自己頂唔順訓咗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nV5df3g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnV5df3g.jpg&h=c67b03f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"024fc3bd8e89a47a9d526a46e8babd78fecc874b","tid":2261014,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"啲光咁嘅形狀 光源應該角度好斜<br />\n即表示光源離地面要好過 <br />\n如果唔係照上去雲層應該只會係圓/橢<br />\n大家可以想像類似Batman支燈咁 <br />\n所以我有諗過係咪有人喺對面山(圖中可見)<br />\n拎幾支燈喺度鳩照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有幾樣嘢<br />\n第一係 咩燈可以上到雲層都咁強光<br />\n起碼支燈要好撚大先<br />\n咁邊撚個又咁得閒凌晨3點拎5支咁嘅燈上高地鳩fing?<br />\n第二係 當初一見嘅時候佢向外散個動作 好齊<br />\n3-4個光一致咁郁<br />\n一係郁嗰啲係練過 而佢哋只係練習緊？<br />\n一係支燈係一大組連住嘅部件？<br />\n<br />\n有冇燈光巴打可以解答到呢個疑惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc33e4044b1a697929eb7f1fbb73de5b663af61d","tid":2261014,"uid":29876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:03:30.000Z","msg":"玩電筒"},{"pid":"1a5f99fe425f07c15111b288f48e47114bd6a0aa","tid":2261014,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"強光電筒都做到同樣效果"},{"pid":"89835af241d5f0f9f4a8aa9608cb92e8163fd564","tid":2261014,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:06:38.000Z","msg":"個窗反射室內光線？"},{"pid":"f55d2a880c6d26a865d3ef992c260a6cb7b3eed2","tid":2261014,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89835af241d5f0f9f4a8aa9608cb92e8163fd564","tid":2261014,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:06:38.000Z","msg":"個窗反射室內光線？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"唔係 間房根本冇啲咁嘅光"},{"pid":"781a6295ec59dbd0b9d644686fd34fa39e3a697b","tid":2261014,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc33e4044b1a697929eb7f1fbb73de5b663af61d","tid":2261014,"uid":29876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:03:30.000Z","msg":"玩電筒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:20:39.000Z","msg":"但啲光唔會好圓好散咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9566c8a0aab61366717d6e94e8a925ce56db844a","tid":2261014,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:25:33.000Z","msg":"幻彩詠啷啷咪藍白色燈"},{"pid":"46820c626b81b301cd0c15abfc611f3c38842f18","tid":2261014,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9566c8a0aab61366717d6e94e8a925ce56db844a","tid":2261014,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:25:33.000Z","msg":"幻彩詠啷啷咪藍白色燈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:29:25.000Z","msg":"但照到青衣？！小遠喎ching"},{"pid":"205ec08bbd2ae4a6d9b7983dcbf80532ac96606e","tid":2261014,"uid":189417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"係 冇錯 俾你發現咗<br />\n咁就召你返去做超級銀河戰士啦"},{"pid":"b2b05751c39448c41e684dabdfe2f13a71f881c9","tid":2261014,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"205ec08bbd2ae4a6d9b7983dcbf80532ac96606e","tid":2261014,"uid":